org.lenskit.api

Interface ResultList

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Collection<Result>, Iterable<Result>, List<Result>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    LenskitResultList
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasicResultList

    public interface ResultList
extends List<Result>

    A list of results from a recommender operation. This is used for operations such as top-N recommendation that produce a list (or occasionally set) of items.
